summary: A game save that I spent time on making. She is level 59, and is adept in one handed. She also uses a few of mods...
descriptionHtml:
As I said, you\'ll need a few of mods. But-- It\'s worth it.

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11447

Female Animation Pack
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29408

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4708

With the female animation pack, you do not want to keep the running animation. That is what the Feminine Running and Dash thing is for. I personally endorse all of these mods I have up there. Vote for those mod creators. Also, you are on the quest to see the Greybeards. I\'m also on XBox and PS3. KMOXX39
